====================  SECTION 9 — ULTRA COMBO PROBLEMS  ====================

THESE COMBINE MULTIPLE TOPICS:

Q621.  READ N, ARRAY, AND PRINT: SUM, AVG, MAX, MIN, PRIME COUNT.
Q622.  READ STRING SENTENCE → LONGEST WORD + VOWEL COUNT + WORD COUNT.
Q623.  READ MATRIX → ROW SUMS + COL SUMS + MAX POSITION + TRANSPOSE.
Q624.  READ NUMBER → CLASSIFY (PRIME / PALINDROME / ARMSTRONG / STRONG).
Q625.  MENU-DRIVEN PROGRAM: NUMBER TOOLS + STRING TOOLS + ARRAY TOOLS.
Q626.  STUDENT MARKS SYSTEM: STORE N STUDENTS (ARRAYS), PRINT RANK LIST.
Q627.  INVENTORY SYSTEM: ADD ITEMS, SELL ITEMS, BILL PRINTING.
Q628.  CONTACT BOOK: ADD / SEARCH / UPDATE / DELETE CONTACTS.
Q629.  QUIZ APP: QUESTIONS ARRAYS + SCORING.
Q630.  EXPENSE TRACKER: CATEGORIES ARRAYS + TOTALS.
Q631.  SEATING BOOKING: BOOK / CANCEL / STATUS (2D).
Q632.  TIC TAC TOE: BOARD + WIN LOGIC + REPLAY.
Q633.  TEXT ANALYZER: CHAR FREQ + WORD FREQ + MOST COMMON.
Q634.  PASSWORD TOOL: VALIDATE + GENERATE + STRENGTH SCORE.
Q635.  NUMBER CONVERTER: DEC / BIN / OCT / HEX (BOTH DIRECTIONS).
Q636.  MATRIX UTILITY: ADD / SUB / MUL / TRANSPOSE / TRIANGULAR / DETERMINANT.
Q637.  GAME: GUESS NUMBER + SCOREBOARD (ARRAYS).
Q638.  PATTERN STUDIO: 15 PATTERNS IN ONE MENU.
Q639.  TIME UTILITY: SECONDS ↔ HH:MM:SS WITH INPUT VALIDATION.
Q640.  BANKING SYSTEM: BALANCE + DEPOSIT + WITHDRAW + TRANSACTION HISTORY.
Q641.  REPORT GENERATOR: ALIGNED OUTPUT FOR STUDENTS.
Q642.  MINI SPREADSHEET: EDIT CELL + SUMS + MAX ROW.
Q643.  TYPING TEST: ACCURACY + SPEED ESTIMATE.
Q644.  CAESAR CIPHER TOOL: ENCRYPT / DECRYPT / FILE-LIKE CONSOLE.
Q645.  PRIME TOOLKIT: RANGE PRIMES + FACTORIZATION + GCD / LCM.
Q646.  DIGIT TOOLKIT: ALL DIGIT OPERATIONS IN ONE.
Q647.  STRING TOOLKIT: 20 OPERATIONS MENU.
Q648.  ARRAY TOOLKIT: 20 OPERATIONS MENU.
Q649.  MATRIX TOOLKIT: 15 OPERATIONS MENU.
Q650.  FINAL MEGA PROGRAM: EVERYTHING COMBINED.

